<section class="col-lg-8 col-md-12 left-column">

<div class="scroll-posts" id="/2019/02/12/the-best-way-to-resist-trump-beto-and-el-paso-show-us-how-its-done/">

<section class="title-container">
<strong>Supporters listen to former Texas Congressman Beto O'Rourke at Chalio Acosta Sports Center at the end of the anti-Trump 'March for Truth' in El Paso, Texas, on February 11, 2019. <span>(Getty/Paul Ratje)</span> </strong>
<h1>The best way to resist Trump? Beto and El Paso show us how it's done</h1>
<h2>Thanks to Beto O'Rourke and the people of El Paso, Trump's first big rally of 2019 was a bust. Resistance, learn!</h2>
</section>
<script type="text/javascript">
